Interface ILocation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLocation, AggNode, GPSPoint, Intersection, RoadNode, ShallowAggNode, XYPoint

    public interface ILocation
    Common interface for all locations, support for latitude and longitude values as well as a projected location.
